   September 12, 2013
   Loved reading this. Brings back a lot of great memories.
   I went to that Fall/Slant 6 show only at the time I had no idea who the
   Fall were. In fact I remember thinking, "who the hell is this
   headlining band that's making me pay more than $6 to see Slant 6?" I
   was so angry I made a point of leaving before the Fall played. Ha! I
   really wish I stuck around now.
